## Función para interés simple


::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code}
interes_simple <- function(a, r, n){
  VF <- a * (1 + r * n)
  return(VF)
}
```
:::


## Ejemplos


::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code}
interes_simple(1000, 0.05, 3)
```

::: {.cell-output .cell-output-stdout}

```
[1] 1150
```


:::

```{.r .cell-code}
